    """Manage Infoblox DNS records.

    Record commands use the active zone unless you pass `--zone`. The active
    zone is resolved from `ib dns zone use`, then IB_ZONE, then the default zone
    saved by `ib configure`.

    \b
    Examples:
      ib dns search app
      ib dns search -g app
      ib dns create a -n app 192.0.2.10 -t 300 -c "Application VIP"
      ib dns create host -n app 192.0.2.10 -t 300
      ib dns create cname -n www app.example.com
      ib dns delete app
    """


